12//
13// Name: cp950 to Unicode table
14// Unicode version: 2.0
15// Table version: 2.01
16// Table format: Format A
17// Date: 1/7/2000
18//
19// Contact: cpxlate@microsoft.com
20//
21// General notes: none
22//
23// Format: Three tab-separated columns
24// Column #1 is the cp950 code (in hex)
25// Column #2 is the Unicode (in hex as 0xXXXX)
26// Column #3 is the Unicode name (follows a comment sign, '#')
27//
28// The entries are in cp950 order
29//
